INVENT@UCA is a co-creation program that brings together students and
professionals.

Its objective: to train students in innovation, creativity and skills for the
21st century while offering solutions to the challenges faced by companies.

Son ambition : créer des change makers au profil international.

Do you want to participate in an immersion in innovation?

Do you want to share a unique experience in co-creation projects?

Joining INVENT@UCA means:

     * Work in a multidisciplinary team on real challenges
     * Develop your skills, especially 21st century essential ones
     * Discover innovation methods (Design Thinking, Effectuation,
       Agile,...)
     * Be accompanied by an enthusiastic team of passionate facilitators
       and experts
     * Develop your professional network, personal branding and value in
       the job market
     * Access to original and enriching events (Hackathon, Expert Corners,
       JAM,...)

INVENT@UCA is also:

     * A certificate accredited by the University Côte d'Azur
     * ECTS credits
     * An innovation bonus
     * A university degree
     * A unique, high value-added experience that you can mention in your
       CV

The INVENT@UCA program can replace an internship or an alternation in your
curriculum.

   Apply

   Finally, the Invent@UCA program provides a real opportunity for
   students to develop their professional network, brand image and value
   in the labour market.

#IMPACT

The Invent Business program (from 1 day to 9 months to find innovative
solutions to a company's problems), the Invent Social Impact program (from 1
day to 3 months to solve a societal problem in open source).

#REFLECT

A series of recurring events and workshops over the two semesters are
scheduled at the beginning of the year. Two-day Expert Corners and two-hour
Shotgun Debates are hosted to showcase trends and approaches to innovation.

#Explore

Stays (from 2 to 5 days depending on the need) as well as expeditions
(solving a societal problem on site) in partnership with NGOs or local
associations.

CALENDAR

INVENT BUSINESS

     * Kick-off (1 day*)
     * 2 x Expert day (1 day*)
     * 2 x JAMS (2 dayas*)
     * Final Demo (1 day*)

INVENT IMPACT SOCIAL

     * Kick-off exploration (1 day*)
     * 4 x Expert day (2 days*)
     * 2x Coaching (half a day*) - 1 x JAM (1 day*)
     * Final Demo (1 day*)

ÉVÈNEMENTS RÉCURRENTS

     * Shotgun débats: Once a month
     * Hackathon/JAM: Twice a year
     * Learning Expedition : Twice a year
     * Expert Corners

   *Format duration

ESPACE VERNASSA

a place devoted to creativity

   350m2 dedicated to creativity and innovation await you in the heart of
   the Saint-Jean-d'Angely campus in Nice. An atypical place with its
   10-metre high glass roof and artistic works, the Vernassa space is 100%
   modular, allowing the organisation of conferences, workshops or working
   groups....

   IFRAME: https://player.vimeo.com/video/293124864

